phpMyAdmin allows database management from web browser.

-> Install required packages
      dnf install php php-mysqlnd php-json php-fpm -y

-> Install phpMyAdmin
      dnf install phpMyAdmin -y

-> Access URL
      http://server-ip/phpmyadmin

-> Why phpMyAdmin?
phpMyAdmin provides:
      -graphical database management
      -table creation
      -query execution
      -user management
